## Quick Reference Checklist

When editing files, verify:

- [ ] Documentation is in `docs/`, not mixed with exercises
- [ ] Exercises are in `exercises/`, with questions separate from answers
- [ ] Answers are at the END of exercise files, not inline
- [ ] Examples are in `examples/`, referenced but not duplicated
- [ ] Links between docs, exercises, and examples are correct
- [ ] No exercise content in documentation files
- [ ] No documentation content in exercise files (only references)

